WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: NQmpemm4FFc

NOTE Language: en

00:00:19.525 --> 00:00:21.672
Yesterday I told you

00:00:21.711 --> 00:00:24.830
how 'Self' is more important

00:00:24.801 --> 00:00:26.925
than anything else

00:00:26.931 --> 00:00:29.715
at the present state of human awareness

00:00:29.703 --> 00:00:33.257
When you are at the human awareness

00:00:33.257 --> 00:00:35.337
first thing that should happen to you

00:00:35.337 --> 00:00:38.297
is to feel your 'Self'.

00:00:38.301 --> 00:00:40.211
As Shri Krishna has said,

00:00:40.211 --> 00:00:43.211
"Atmane atmane thushtaha."

00:00:43.223 --> 00:00:47.110
Unless and until you reach your Atma, your Spirit,

00:00:47.129 --> 00:00:50.400
you are not going to get the satisfaction

00:00:50.400 --> 00:00:54.930
of achieving anything.

00:00:54.944 --> 00:00:58.698
Because Kundalini, which you see here

00:00:58.707 --> 00:01:04.368
seated in the triangular bone

00:01:04.368 --> 00:01:09.668
which we call as the sacrum

00:01:09.678 --> 00:01:12.178
that means, Greek knew about it.

00:01:12.198 --> 00:01:15.402
Greek knew about the sacrum bone.

00:01:15.415 --> 00:01:20.172
Otherwise they would not have called it as sacrum, means sacred.

00:01:20.179 --> 00:01:23.409
Even when I went to Athens I was surprised

00:01:23.409 --> 00:01:26.819
that Athena, the word 'Atha' comes from Sanskrit,

00:01:26.807 --> 00:01:30.999
means primordial. And she had a snake like thing

00:01:31.004 --> 00:01:33.799
in Her hand with all the chakras.

00:01:33.782 --> 00:01:36.165
So the Greeks knew about it.

00:01:36.165 --> 00:01:37.536
And when I talked to them

00:01:37.537 --> 00:01:40.367
they told Me, that it is a fact.

00:01:40.367 --> 00:01:43.527
that Indians came much before Alexander.

00:01:43.527 --> 00:01:44.887
We had a rapport with Indians

00:01:44.886 --> 00:01:46.832
much before Alexander

00:01:46.828 --> 00:01:50.073
and they told us about the Primordial Mother

00:01:50.083 --> 00:01:51.749
and Her three powers.

00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:54.743
It is very amazing how they knew all about it.

00:01:54.746 --> 00:02:01.896
And then it all got lost because of the extroversion,

00:02:01.892 --> 00:02:09.102
a moving out from reality.

00:02:09.095 --> 00:02:13.591
So this bone, sacrum bone contains

00:02:13.601 --> 00:02:21.161
or here resides the Kundalini in three and a half coil

00:02:21.161 --> 00:02:25.870
This is the power of our pure desire.

00:02:25.869 --> 00:02:30.569
The pure desire is the desire, when it is manifested

00:02:30.583 --> 00:02:33.280
should give you full satisfaction.

00:02:33.295 --> 00:02:37.130
For example, some people seek it in power.

00:02:37.163 --> 00:02:38.753
They indulge in power.

00:02:38.753 --> 00:02:40.713
Some seek it in possessions.

00:02:40.703 --> 00:02:44.019
Some seek it in other things.

00:02:44.022 --> 00:02:49.389
But all these seekings do not give them satisfaction

00:02:49.389 --> 00:02:52.357
If they could give satisfaction

00:02:52.377 --> 00:02:57.587
then there would have been no problem.

00:02:57.564 --> 00:03:01.612
Because once you buy a car then you want to buy something else

00:03:01.609 --> 00:03:04.109
and then you buy…want to buy something else.

00:03:04.169 --> 00:03:08.282
You start moving from one to another and as Economics says

00:03:08.307 --> 00:03:11.401
that in particular a want is satiable

00:03:11.409 --> 00:03:13.318
but not in general.

00:03:13.318 --> 00:03:15.339
So we have to understand, that the wants

00:03:15.339 --> 00:03:17.489
that we have, the desires we have,

00:03:17.483 --> 00:03:21.335
are not pure desires, but are impure desires

00:03:21.337 --> 00:03:23.229
and when we deal with them,

00:03:23.237 --> 00:03:25.448
we never get that satisfaction.

00:03:25.443 --> 00:03:28.474
For example somebody wants to do something

00:03:28.492 --> 00:03:31.738
he does it but doesn’t get any satisfaction out of it.

00:03:31.738 --> 00:03:34.462
The only way you can get satisfaction is

00:03:34.452 --> 00:03:38.542
that you become one with the Divine.

00:03:38.562 --> 00:03:43.414
And this power of desire which is a pure desire is

00:03:43.404 --> 00:03:47.134
residing in each and everybody’s triangular bone.

00:03:47.131 --> 00:03:48.614
But we are lost.

00:03:48.614 --> 00:03:51.114
We are seeking our pleasures,

00:03:51.114 --> 00:03:53.671
our joys into wrong things

00:03:53.658 --> 00:03:57.123
We think that by doing this or by doing that,

00:03:57.123 --> 00:03:59.623
by buying this or becoming that

00:03:59.623 --> 00:04:02.600
we will be completely, fully satisfied,

00:04:02.596 --> 00:04:05.096
which we ultimately discover.

00:04:05.106 --> 00:04:07.036
In a evolutionary stage

00:04:07.036 --> 00:04:09.220
such people when they discover

00:04:09.220 --> 00:04:11.720
that the joy is not in all these things;

00:04:11.734 --> 00:04:14.446
there is no happiness in this kind of thing;

00:04:14.450 --> 00:04:16.030
we have to go beyond this.

00:04:16.026 --> 00:04:18.300
Once they discover this then they become

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:20.450
a special category of people.

00:04:20.450 --> 00:04:22.950
And these special categories of people

00:04:22.950 --> 00:04:24.670
are the seekers.

00:04:24.670 --> 00:04:28.900
Of course today I find so many seekers are lost.

00:04:28.895 --> 00:04:31.395
Especially in America they are lost in various ways.

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:33.930
We would say in all the cults,

00:04:33.944 --> 00:04:39.504
or in all other things like drugs, or homosexuality

00:04:39.525 --> 00:04:42.658
or whatever you may call it, they are lost into these.

00:04:42.682 --> 00:04:45.668
Into violence, many are indulging into violence.

00:04:45.668 --> 00:04:47.396
Or doing all kinds of things

00:04:47.401 --> 00:04:50.396
which are not for their ascent,

00:04:50.396 --> 00:04:53.816
but are degrading and will take them down

00:04:53.816 --> 00:04:56.446
not to their seeking, but to their hell.

00:04:56.443 --> 00:04:58.324
But it is happening today.

00:04:58.331 --> 00:04:59.663
You can see it very clearly.

00:04:59.663 --> 00:05:00.781
It is happening

00:05:00.781 --> 00:05:04.671
because human beings do not understand

00:05:04.681 --> 00:05:08.339
that human awareness is a transitory phase,

00:05:08.331 --> 00:05:10.361
you have to go beyond it.

00:05:10.371 --> 00:05:13.121
And that beyond stage, the stage we have to reach

00:05:13.121 --> 00:05:15.562
is the stage of your 'Self'.

00:05:15.569 --> 00:05:16.832
To begin with

00:05:16.832 --> 00:05:19.629
you have to become first of all 'Self Realised'.

00:05:19.618 --> 00:05:22.276
Meaning you are to be 'Born Again'.

00:05:22.272 --> 00:05:23.823
And to be born again

00:05:23.828 --> 00:05:27.993
you have to allow the Kundalini to work it out.

00:05:27.994 --> 00:05:30.898
So what do we do as people said,

00:05:30.886 --> 00:05:33.608
I told you yesterday, it is effortless.

00:05:33.609 --> 00:05:35.806
It is without any money.

00:05:35.816 --> 00:05:38.811
It just happens spontaneously.

00:05:38.811 --> 00:05:40.156
Now it happens that

00:05:40.156 --> 00:05:43.116
an enlightened light can enlighten another light.

00:05:43.098 --> 00:05:44.876
In the same way

00:05:44.876 --> 00:05:46.556
I may be able to enlighten you

00:05:46.528 --> 00:05:48.766
but you can enlighten many others.

00:05:48.766 --> 00:05:50.428
Like in India we have someone

00:05:50.418 --> 00:05:53.338
who has enlightened 10,000 people.

00:05:53.338 --> 00:05:55.388
and has done so much good to people,

00:05:55.388 --> 00:05:57.368
that it is amazing.

00:05:57.368 --> 00:06:00.850
Even there are people like the President of India,

00:06:00.841 --> 00:06:05.160
we can say the President of the High Court

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:08.207
Judge of the Hague High Court

00:06:08.207 --> 00:06:09.537
which is the World High Court,

00:06:09.537 --> 00:06:10.538
The president of that,

00:06:10.538 --> 00:06:11.667
He's got his Realisation

00:06:11.697 --> 00:06:13.267
and he's a Sahaja Yogi

00:06:13.250 --> 00:06:15.606
So we have people of that calibre

00:06:15.620 --> 00:06:17.096
who are Sahaja Yogis.

00:06:17.096 --> 00:06:18.876
and who have felt the vibrations

00:06:18.876 --> 00:06:20.416
who have become Self Realised.

00:06:20.414 --> 00:06:24.366
But they are very humble people, extremely humble people.

00:06:24.391 --> 00:06:27.441
Indians are basically humble and they know

00:06:27.441 --> 00:06:29.671
who is a saint and who is not a saint.

00:06:29.681 --> 00:06:31.994
They are so sensitive that they know

00:06:31.991 --> 00:06:33.974
who is a saint and who is not a saint.

00:06:33.974 --> 00:06:38.284
But in the West, as we have now lost our power

00:06:38.284 --> 00:06:40.634
to feel the saintliness in a person

00:06:40.613 --> 00:06:43.936
we do not know who is a saint, who is not a saint.

00:06:43.936 --> 00:06:49.283
So the first thing that has to happen to you to understand who is a saint, who is not a saint,

00:06:49.298 --> 00:06:52.878
is first to get your Realisation.

00:06:52.898 --> 00:06:56.736
Without the spirit expressing itself

00:06:56.770 --> 00:06:59.746
into your awareness, into your attention,

00:06:59.749 --> 00:07:03.646
you cannot make out who is a saint, or who is not a saint.

00:07:03.655 --> 00:07:06.566
Like they crucified Christ for no reason at all

00:07:06.568 --> 00:07:10.533
and they worshipped Hitler.

00:07:10.524 --> 00:07:13.503
The Jews, they refused to accept Christ,

00:07:13.504 --> 00:07:16.783
they refused. They said, no we don’t accept Christ,

00:07:16.780 --> 00:07:19.693
because Christ said that I am dying for your sins.

00:07:19.690 --> 00:07:26.679
They said, no we don’t believe in that. We must suffer. So they suffered.

00:07:26.702 --> 00:07:30.460
They had sufferings.  If you ask for suffering you’ll have sufferings.

00:07:30.460 --> 00:07:31.852
But if they had accepted Christ

00:07:31.852 --> 00:07:33.630
at least one thing would have happened

00:07:33.652 --> 00:07:36.080
they would not have suffered.

00:07:36.051 --> 00:07:41.473
They asked for suffering. They thought unless and until we suffer we cannot go to God.

00:07:41.483 --> 00:07:44.591
This was a very wrong idea.  Because Christ himself was a Jew.

00:07:44.588 --> 00:07:47.452
Himself He took birth among the Jews.

00:07:47.456 --> 00:07:49.826
And it was the Jews He came to save.

00:07:49.826 --> 00:07:54.116
But they are the ones who refused to accept Him,

00:07:54.103 --> 00:07:58.742
because they were blinded. They didn't want to see the point.

00:07:58.732 --> 00:08:02.229
In the same way it has happened in every century.

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:06.319
Anytime any incarnation came people did not want to accept.

00:08:06.351 --> 00:08:10.739
Not in India, I would say. Indians are much more sensitive to spirituality,

00:08:10.751 --> 00:08:12.724
because they are not so much materialistic.

00:08:12.729 --> 00:08:19.609
They understand, because we have been for ages seeking and seeking from… traditionally

00:08:19.609 --> 00:08:22.109
So we know what this seeking is.

00:08:22.085 --> 00:08:25.744
What it means.  For Me it’s not difficult to talk to them about Kundalini.

00:08:25.732 --> 00:08:27.829
There I start on a different level altogether,

00:08:27.810 --> 00:08:32.309
because they know everything whatever I’m talking, they know already, what it is.

00:08:32.309 --> 00:08:36.799
May be not in the cities where the people are westernised. But they know.

00:08:36.770 --> 00:08:39.270
But for other people I have to start it from A to Z.

00:08:39.436 --> 00:08:47.203
So this is the Kundalini. We have got it. Three and a half coils, and it has a mathematical calculation.

00:08:47.228 --> 00:08:54.033
Now it’s only Indians and Buddhists from Indians I would say believe in the non-being.

00:08:54.036 --> 00:08:56.963
They believe there’s a non-being; being and non-being.

00:08:56.973 --> 00:08:59.473
What is that state of non-being?

00:08:59.506 --> 00:09:06.484
When you become the non-being means when you go beyond your conditioning and ego then you become the non-being.

00:09:06.556 --> 00:09:10.896
And once you become the non-being then nothing can touch you.

00:09:10.928 --> 00:09:17.262
As I told you yesterday…who are standing in the water have fear of getting drowned in the water,

00:09:17.251 --> 00:09:26.613
but if you go to the boat then you start seeing that the water is down below it is not going to touch you.

00:09:26.622 --> 00:09:31.773
That state has to be achieved, is the non-being, is the fourth dimension within us.

00:09:31.784 --> 00:09:36.013
This is called also in Sanskrit as Turya dasha.

00:09:36.022 --> 00:09:39.516
Now you might say why in India, these people discovered all that.

00:09:39.750 --> 00:09:43.126
See now the reason is India is a very ancient country.

00:09:43.126 --> 00:09:48.375
And there we didn’t have these problems that you had to face when you came to America.

00:09:48.381 --> 00:09:52.065
You had to face the nature to begin with. Our nature is very kind.

00:09:52.072 --> 00:09:57.304
You can live under a tree, eat the fruits of the forest and can enjoy ourselves.

00:09:57.315 --> 00:10:03.987
We don’t need much in that country to cover ourselves or to have any elaboration.

00:10:03.995 --> 00:10:08.855
So the attention has been always inside to find out why are we here?

00:10:08.879 --> 00:10:11.875
What are we doing here?  Are we wasting our life?

00:10:11.875 --> 00:10:14.955
Are we doing any harm to ourselves or to others?

00:10:14.953 --> 00:10:20.500
Is it alright to exist as human beings or is there anything beyond?

00:10:20.517 --> 00:10:24.420
This search has been there for thousands and thousands of years.

00:10:24.431 --> 00:10:27.311
And because of this seeking

00:10:27.316 --> 00:10:30.459
they have been able to reach, right conclusions

00:10:30.486 --> 00:10:33.509
that there is this Kundalini within us.

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:36.092
And this Kundalini is to be awakened.

00:10:36.092 --> 00:10:37.609
And if She is awakened

00:10:37.608 --> 00:10:41.869
then you can become 'Self' very easily.

00:10:41.874 --> 00:10:45.419
And this was the job I had to do.

00:10:45.419 --> 00:10:47.919
For that I had to work very hard

00:10:47.919 --> 00:10:49.719
for days together to understand

00:10:49.704 --> 00:10:52.009
what was the problem with human beings,

00:10:52.011 --> 00:10:53.739
the permutations and combinations

00:10:53.739 --> 00:10:56.549
of problems that they had.

00:10:56.540 --> 00:10:59.691
And somehow I managed it, I think.

00:10:59.691 --> 00:11:02.616
Now en masse Realisation is possible.

00:11:02.616 --> 00:11:05.651
Yesterday despite some people being mischievous

00:11:05.645 --> 00:11:06.907
you did get Realisation.

00:11:06.915 --> 00:11:08.307
This is God's work

00:11:08.307 --> 00:11:10.587
and God's work will go on.

00:11:10.615 --> 00:11:12.457
Whether some people come and trouble you,

00:11:12.444 --> 00:11:13.494
makes no difference.

00:11:13.492 --> 00:11:15.734
They are just like mosquitoes.

00:11:15.726 --> 00:11:19.444
They come and go away, has no meaning at all.

00:11:19.444 --> 00:11:21.944
Because you see God’s work is much greater

00:11:21.944 --> 00:11:24.404
than what they think of themselves.

00:11:24.402 --> 00:11:26.902
So it doesn't matter what happens

00:11:26.902 --> 00:11:29.133
or what people say or talk.

00:11:29.142 --> 00:11:30.793
The God's work will go on

00:11:30.793 --> 00:11:32.857
But you must know it is a living work.

00:11:32.853 --> 00:11:34.703
It's not a plastic thing.

00:11:34.703 --> 00:11:37.203
You can produce thousands of plastic flowers

00:11:37.203 --> 00:11:38.471
very easily,

00:11:38.482 --> 00:11:41.982
but you cannot produce one single living flower.

00:11:42.016 --> 00:11:45.742
So when this living force has to act it takes time.

00:11:45.782 --> 00:11:48.282
And it will take time, gradually it will grow.

00:11:48.282 --> 00:11:49.820
And you'll be surprised that

00:11:49.810 --> 00:11:52.434
gradually it will grow so beautifully,

00:11:52.434 --> 00:11:53.500
that suddenly you'll find

00:11:53.518 --> 00:11:57.650
lots of people coming up and becoming.

00:11:57.650 --> 00:11:58.720
Because in Sahaja Yoga

00:11:58.720 --> 00:12:00.750
what you become is important.

00:12:00.755 --> 00:12:02.385
It’s the actualisation.

00:12:02.410 --> 00:12:05.795
It is not some certificate or some organisation

00:12:05.795 --> 00:12:07.810
that you belong to some organisation

00:12:07.810 --> 00:12:09.555
or there is some certificate.

00:12:09.545 --> 00:12:12.045
But it is what you become.

00:12:12.045 --> 00:12:14.545
Your becoming is important

00:12:14.545 --> 00:12:16.373
If you cannot become something

00:12:16.361 --> 00:12:18.633
the you are no good in Sahaja Yoga.

00:12:18.633 --> 00:12:19.923
Many people who come to us

00:12:19.923 --> 00:12:22.453
we find they improve a lot

00:12:22.457 --> 00:12:24.608
and they become very great also.

00:12:24.614 --> 00:12:26.238
But some people do not.

00:12:26.249 --> 00:12:27.668
They just waste it.

00:12:27.679 --> 00:12:30.164
Energy is all wasted whatever you try they do not.

00:12:30.164 --> 00:12:32.664
Sometimes they are so conditioned

00:12:32.664 --> 00:12:34.619
that we cannot improve them.

00:12:34.624 --> 00:12:36.874
There we feel helpless about them

00:12:36.876 --> 00:12:39.214
because they do not want to corporate also.

00:12:39.214 --> 00:12:41.714
And also they have many pressures on them.

00:12:41.686 --> 00:12:45.544
But 90% people go up very well

00:12:45.524 --> 00:12:49.014
and they manifest whatever they have achieved

00:12:49.014 --> 00:12:52.284
Now the main thing is to understand

00:12:52.284 --> 00:12:55.514
that this mechanism exists with us.

00:12:55.504 --> 00:12:58.004
This energy exists within us.

00:12:58.004 --> 00:13:01.614
Now this is like a hypothesis for you.

00:13:01.642 --> 00:13:04.243
You need not accept it. It’s a hypothesis

00:13:04.243 --> 00:13:06.416
as one would put to a scientist.

00:13:06.409 --> 00:13:08.909
But scientist must have an open…open mind.

00:13:08.909 --> 00:13:10.399
They shouldn’t have a closed mind.

00:13:10.399 --> 00:13:11.449
if you have a barrier

00:13:11.449 --> 00:13:14.059
you cannot put anything before them.

00:13:14.059 --> 00:13:16.559
If they are scientist they will have an open mind

00:13:16.539 --> 00:13:18.499
to listen to My hypothesis.

00:13:18.493 --> 00:13:22.779
And if it could be proved, if it could be proved

00:13:22.761 --> 00:13:25.261
then you have to accept it.

00:13:25.261 --> 00:13:26.502
If it is...  doesn't prove,

00:13:26.502 --> 00:13:29.482
then you can say all right that's not proved so far.

00:13:29.482 --> 00:13:30.312
All right!

00:13:30.299 --> 00:13:32.799
So you have to wait and have patience with it.

00:13:32.799 --> 00:13:35.992
This is what it is in simple words

00:13:35.999 --> 00:13:38.499
that I cannot be forced on you.

00:13:38.499 --> 00:13:43.153
It cannot be humbled before you.

00:13:43.153 --> 00:13:45.653
You have to ask for it.

00:13:45.653 --> 00:13:48.473
Nobody can force you that you can become.

00:13:48.477 --> 00:13:50.977
I cannot guarantee yesterday I said. It's a fact.

00:13:50.977 --> 00:13:53.817
But still so many people got their realisation,

00:13:53.817 --> 00:13:56.327
felt the cool breeze and felt the cool

00:13:56.327 --> 00:13:57.407
breeze out of the head.

00:13:57.402 --> 00:13:59.797
This you cannot do otherwise.

00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:02.300
All other things you can do but this you cannot do,

00:14:02.338 --> 00:14:04.838
is to take out cool breeze of your head

00:14:04.861 --> 00:14:07.768
which is a factual thing and experienced.

00:14:07.768 --> 00:14:10.488
But as I told you, that we live mentally

00:14:10.488 --> 00:14:13.288
much more than we live with reality.

00:14:13.288 --> 00:14:15.233
And mental projection can be anything

00:14:15.215 --> 00:14:16.865
like a person who murders someone.

00:14:16.868 --> 00:14:18.225
He has justification,

00:14:18.225 --> 00:14:20.725
I murdered someone because of this and this,

00:14:20.725 --> 00:14:22.179
but that justification

00:14:22.184 --> 00:14:24.189
does not allow you to get out of law.

00:14:24.194 --> 00:14:25.995
Does it? No.

00:14:25.995 --> 00:14:28.495
