00:29:38.607 --> 00:29:39.680
upward, like that

00:29:39.680 --> 00:29:42.180
So all your attention which is outside goes inside.

00:29:42.180 --> 00:29:45.780
And when it pierces through from here,

00:29:45.780 --> 00:29:48.700
this piercing makes the attention subtle

00:29:48.700 --> 00:29:56.060
because the subtle that is around which you do not feel normally starts penetrating into it.

00:29:56.060 --> 00:29:58.436
It starts covering your attention.

00:29:58.430 --> 00:30:01.786
And that’s how we say now your attention is enlightened.

00:30:01.796 --> 00:30:08.796
And now it is enlightened. Not just talk but it becomes enlightened with collective consciousness.

00:30:08.796 --> 00:30:12.236
You become collectively conscious.

00:30:12.226 --> 00:30:21.721
Then such people when they talk, when they talk have such a personality, such a knowledge.

00:30:21.741 --> 00:30:24.412
They become knowledge. They have no problems.

00:30:24.412 --> 00:30:28.286
They become knowledge because they become the absolute knowledge.

00:30:28.298 --> 00:30:32.126
But it is for you to decide. What are you seeking in life?

00:30:32.126 --> 00:30:35.898
What do you want in life?  What is your life worth?

00:30:35.916 --> 00:30:42.766
If you want to cheapen your life, waste it for something very cheap and ordinary and useless then you can go ahead.

00:30:42.793 --> 00:30:45.993
But if you think your life is important as a human being, it should be,

00:30:46.023 --> 00:30:51.343
because you have become from amoeba to this stage as human being not to waste it.

00:30:51.368 --> 00:30:55.896
Not to throw it away, uselessly, but to become the Spirit.

00:30:55.896 --> 00:30:58.396
That is what you have come on this Earth for

00:30:58.396 --> 00:31:01.218
and that's what should happen to you.

00:31:01.218 --> 00:31:05.077
Now the main problem with human beings is

00:31:05.101 --> 00:31:07.007
that there are barriers we have got.

00:31:07.007 --> 00:31:12.161
To accept anything we have barriers. But there is nothing to be accepted.

00:31:12.163 --> 00:31:16.117
In Sahaja yoga you need not accept anything what so ever but you should also not deny.

00:31:16.117 --> 00:31:20.269
If you deny I cannot raise your Kundalini. I cannot.

00:31:20.267 --> 00:31:24.809
You should allow your mind to be open to get realised.

00:31:24.809 --> 00:31:26.807
Because one reason is there,

00:31:26.801 --> 00:31:28.344
why you have to do that more,

00:31:28.336 --> 00:31:30.716
because you do not know about Kundalini

00:31:30.700 --> 00:31:33.516
People told Me they don’t even know what Self Realisation is.

00:31:33.517 --> 00:31:37.597
Imagine in India when My grandchild was born

00:31:37.597 --> 00:31:42.547
we had our astrologer in My husband’s place,

00:31:42.571 --> 00:31:45.397
about two thousand miles away

00:31:45.397 --> 00:31:47.128
from where the child was born.

00:31:47.128 --> 00:31:48.644
He sent a telegram saying that

00:31:48.644 --> 00:31:51.301
this child has found her guru,

00:31:51.298 --> 00:31:53.218
sadguru in the household.

00:31:53.218 --> 00:31:55.718
It was such a great thing to find a sadguru

00:31:55.718 --> 00:31:58.728
who will give realisation to the child.

00:31:58.738 --> 00:32:01.238
To us it is the most important thing.

00:32:01.238 --> 00:32:03.738
In a horoscope the first thing they’ll ask,

00:32:03.738 --> 00:32:06.138
"Will, shall we get Self Realisation

00:32:06.138 --> 00:32:07.448
in this life time or not?"

00:32:07.448 --> 00:32:09.436
Then they will say, "All right,

00:32:09.436 --> 00:32:11.008
this life left, time be mine.

00:32:11.032 --> 00:32:13.527
May be next lifetime.” Then they’ll think, “Oh God,

00:32:13.527 --> 00:32:17.907
we have to wait one life time more."

00:32:17.907 --> 00:32:20.987
And all the action is surrounding that.

00:32:20.987 --> 00:32:22.037
The whole behaviour

00:32:22.067 --> 00:32:24.817
that you must try to check your attention.

00:32:24.827 --> 00:32:27.917
Chitta nirodh, try to check your attention.

00:32:27.927 --> 00:32:30.216
Wherever it wants to go just keep it out.

00:32:30.207 --> 00:32:34.426
While here it is, “What’s wrong?" "So what?”

00:32:34.436 --> 00:32:36.936
If you want you jump in the sea. "So what?"

00:32:36.936 --> 00:32:38.896
"Who are you to tell us?"

00:32:38.896 --> 00:32:39.856
It is not that.

00:32:39.856 --> 00:32:42.566
There it is, you must control your attention.

00:32:42.570 --> 00:32:45.950
Control your attention! Keep the attention pure!

00:32:45.972 --> 00:32:49.360
If your attention is not pure at the time of Realisation

00:32:49.360 --> 00:32:51.860
there will be a problem

00:32:51.860 --> 00:32:54.990
It is just a different attitude towards life in India.

00:32:54.990 --> 00:32:56.483
If somebody is angry

00:32:56.483 --> 00:32:59.033
here people always say. "I hate you."

00:32:59.010 --> 00:33:01.170
I mean in India if a child says like that

00:33:01.170 --> 00:33:03.670
he will have two slaps on the face.

00:33:03.666 --> 00:33:05.428
Its regarded bad manners to

00:33:05.448 --> 00:33:07.638
even to think like that, that you hate anyone

00:33:07.636 --> 00:33:14.288
To hate anyone is a sign of degraded personality.

00:33:14.308 --> 00:33:16.808
I mean it’s very common with Indian people.

00:33:16.808 --> 00:33:18.968
Whatever you know of Indians are the people

00:33:18.968 --> 00:33:19.888
who are uprooted,

00:33:19.888 --> 00:33:21.478
who have come here to make dollars.

00:33:21.468 --> 00:33:23.028
They are different people.

00:33:23.028 --> 00:33:25.008
They are sort of sieved out.

00:33:25.028 --> 00:33:27.098
But the people who are in India,

00:33:27.105 --> 00:33:28.118
now we have here

00:33:28.111 --> 00:33:31.168
at least 20% people who have been to India.

00:33:31.188 --> 00:33:33.258
You can ask them.

00:33:33.264 --> 00:33:38.935
To them generosity is a quality.

00:33:38.935 --> 00:33:40.484
Righteousness is a quality.

00:33:40.488 --> 00:33:43.838
Purity is a quality. Quietude is a quality.

00:33:43.838 --> 00:33:45.958
Peaceful nature is a quality.

00:33:45.978 --> 00:33:47.938
They do not boast of their angers

00:33:47.948 --> 00:33:49.948
and they do not boast of their hatred at all.

00:33:49.926 --> 00:33:53.227
I mean it is never, never, never done.

00:33:53.221 --> 00:33:55.481
Even if somebody hates he will

00:33:55.496 --> 00:33:58.551
not say that, "I hate you."

00:33:58.547 --> 00:34:00.287
I mean it took some time for Me

00:34:00.283 --> 00:34:02.783
to even say this sentence to people

00:34:02.787 --> 00:34:06.069
like it is something prohibited.

00:34:06.067 --> 00:34:09.529
Because it's your tongue gets spoiled.

00:34:09.527 --> 00:34:12.027
If your tongue is spoiled and is impure

00:34:12.027 --> 00:34:16.637
then whatever you say becomes untruth.

00:34:16.627 --> 00:34:19.127
Your tongue must be pure.

00:34:19.127 --> 00:34:22.457
You should not say something which is not true.

00:34:22.457 --> 00:34:24.957
In the sense, true doesn't mean that

00:34:24.957 --> 00:34:27.457
supposing somebody is a person,

00:34:27.443 --> 00:34:29.943
who to your mind is not a good person.

00:34:29.943 --> 00:34:32.894
You shouldn’t say that. Need not say that

00:34:32.894 --> 00:34:35.394
you are not a good person. You just keep quiet.

00:34:35.393 --> 00:34:36.253
Let him discover,

00:34:36.253 --> 00:34:41.513
because if he is bad, he will suffer himself.

00:34:41.514 --> 00:34:43.843
This is a common attitude.

00:34:43.844 --> 00:34:45.283
I am not talking for Indians,

00:34:45.293 --> 00:34:47.493
but I must say for Spiritual life,

00:34:47.483 --> 00:34:49.653
one has to learn from them.

00:34:49.654 --> 00:34:51.576
Some of them who were thugs

00:34:51.584 --> 00:34:54.084
must have come here to loot you. That's a different point.

00:34:54.084 --> 00:34:56.896
I mean I am sorry for that. I am sorry.

00:34:56.896 --> 00:34:59.776
But I also blame you for your naiveness.

00:34:59.776 --> 00:35:02.276
I came much before that. But I said

00:35:02.276 --> 00:35:03.996
you are not to pay to anyone any money.

00:35:04.007 --> 00:35:06.507
Nobody listened to Me. They didn't like me

00:35:06.507 --> 00:35:08.857
at all, when I said that.

00:35:08.857 --> 00:35:11.357
So you had to suffer.

00:35:11.335 --> 00:35:14.086
I know it was wrong, but it happened.

00:35:14.086 --> 00:35:17.482
Now at least people should realise

00:35:17.494 --> 00:35:22.497
that purity can only be achieved

00:35:22.514 --> 00:35:24.437
through Self Realisation.

00:35:24.456 --> 00:35:26.767
Innocence can be awakened within you

00:35:26.767 --> 00:35:29.027
on the first chakra.

00:35:29.017 --> 00:35:31.887
On the first chakra you develop innocence.

00:35:31.892 --> 00:35:34.942
In the second chakra you develop creativity.

00:35:34.938 --> 00:35:36.832
I’ve known people who never used to sing

00:35:36.832 --> 00:35:38.392
have started singing very well.

00:35:38.392 --> 00:35:39.872
Who never used to create anything

00:35:39.881 --> 00:35:42.672
have started creating beautiful paintings.

00:35:42.672 --> 00:35:47.292
They have become great painters now, very well known painters, musicians.

00:35:47.293 --> 00:35:56.479
Those who were never doing architecture have become great architects and who  have never done any interior decoration have achieved a lot.

00:35:56.479 --> 00:36:05.749
So, to say that we are very creative one must know that you have limited energy and for that you have to be connected to the mains.

00:36:05.749 --> 00:36:08.249
So, all the time the energy is flowing into you.

00:36:08.249 --> 00:36:14.849
Then on top of that is the third centre, which is the centre of your seeking.

00:36:14.842 --> 00:36:19.669
So whatever you were seeking was not alright.

00:36:19.642 --> 00:36:23.049
But you do get your material well being. No doubt.

00:36:23.049 --> 00:36:29.322
You do get your material well being but up to a point where you feel absolutely satisfied about it.

00:36:29.323 --> 00:36:31.823
You don’t need anything anymore.

00:36:31.823 --> 00:36:39.003
You also get a great blessing of dignity and divinity.

00:36:39.021 --> 00:36:44.483
You get a proper understanding of your being. You become like a king.

00:36:44.483 --> 00:36:49.901
For a king what we call the emperor, he doesn’t need anything.

00:36:49.891 --> 00:36:56.913
For example as you know I am born of a very rich family and it’s a royal family and My husband also is a very rich man.

00:36:56.912 --> 00:37:03.163
It’s alright, we live in a very great comfort no doubt. But I can sleep anywhere. I can sleep on the street,

00:37:03.163 --> 00:37:05.663
I can live anywhere. I am not bothered where I live,

00:37:05.663 --> 00:37:09.533
what I do, how I move. I have no problem.

00:37:09.530 --> 00:37:13.543
Because if you are the emperor,

00:37:13.543 --> 00:37:15.593
you don't ask for anything. Do you?

00:37:15.593 --> 00:37:19.411
If you get the food, alright, if you don't, alright.

00:37:19.413 --> 00:37:22.293
If you like some food, or don’t like food

00:37:22.283 --> 00:37:24.783
somebody says, I have said, “I don’t know what I ate in the morning.

00:37:24.790 --> 00:37:26.763
I don’t know what I am going to eat now.

00:37:26.770 --> 00:37:29.270
I don’t know if I had my lunch or not.

00:37:29.270 --> 00:37:30.210
If I've had, all right.

00:37:30.210 --> 00:37:32.710
Otherwise you can do what you like.

00:37:32.697 --> 00:37:35.197
It’s that simple. Your body becomes your slave.

00:37:35.197 --> 00:37:37.697
You can lie down anywhere you feel like.

00:37:37.697 --> 00:37:39.447
You can do any amount of travelling.

00:37:39.467 --> 00:37:42.847
You can do thousand and one things.

00:37:42.847 --> 00:37:45.347
You become so dynamic.

00:37:45.347 --> 00:37:49.066
That happens when your Lakshmi Tattwa is arisen.

00:37:49.066 --> 00:37:51.566
There are four Lakshmi Tattwas within us.

00:37:51.566 --> 00:37:53.636
The first is the Lakshmi Tattwa,

00:37:53.628 --> 00:37:57.546
where you become a person very dignified

00:37:57.536 --> 00:38:02.266
and endowed with material comforts.

00:38:02.286 --> 00:38:04.786
But comfort which kill you is not there.

00:38:04.786 --> 00:38:08.741
Comfort means you are materially no more bothered.

00:38:08.721 --> 00:38:12.161
You get jobs. In London we have so many jobless people.

00:38:12.161 --> 00:38:14.661
But in Sahaja yoga all those who are there,

00:38:14.661 --> 00:38:17.593
all of them have got jobs.  All of them!

00:38:17.593 --> 00:38:20.771
It's difficult to find one person who hasn’t got the job.

00:38:20.761 --> 00:38:24.171
Moreover it is compulsory in Sahaja yoga that those who stay in the ashram

00:38:24.195 --> 00:38:26.161
must have some jobs.

00:38:26.175 --> 00:38:28.675
We have tried to allow some people to come without that

00:38:28.675 --> 00:38:32.081
but we had very bad experiences of such people.

00:38:32.081 --> 00:38:35.871
So all those who are living on dole or some sort of a thing,

00:38:35.873 --> 00:38:37.721
we don’t allow them to come in the ashram.

00:38:37.721 --> 00:38:42.713
And you will be surprised that as soon as they join Sahaja Yoga they get jobs.

00:38:42.711 --> 00:38:45.211
They get better and better jobs

00:38:45.211 --> 00:38:49.181
because Krishna has said, "Yoga kshema vahamyaham."

00:38:49.181 --> 00:38:53.221
"When you get your yoga, your well being will be looked after."

00:38:53.241 --> 00:38:55.741
He didn’t say, "Kshema yoga," he didn’t say

00:38:55.741 --> 00:38:58.551
"I’ll look after your well being and then you go to yoga."

00:38:58.554 --> 00:39:01.671
No! First yoga. "Yoga kshema vahamyaham."

00:39:01.671 --> 00:39:04.171
"First you get the yoga and then the kshema will work out."

00:39:04.171 --> 00:39:07.721
That’s what happens to you on the Nabhi Chakra,

00:39:07.721 --> 00:39:11.171
which is very important. But Raja Lakshmi that is

00:39:11.171 --> 00:39:13.221
you become like a king.

00:39:13.241 --> 00:39:16.131
That you become Gruha Lakshmi or Gruhastha

00:39:16.131 --> 00:39:18.186
means you become a house holder.

00:39:18.221 --> 00:39:20.721
You become a good wife and a good husband.

00:39:20.721 --> 00:39:24.166
You develop proper feelings for each other.

00:39:24.166 --> 00:39:26.666
And you develop proper feelings for your children.

00:39:26.666 --> 00:39:29.686
You improve your societies through that essence

00:39:29.686 --> 00:39:35.516
if it is born in you that you understand the importance of a good family life.

00:39:35.516 --> 00:39:39.546
And that automatically happens. You don’t have to tell anybody.

00:39:39.546 --> 00:39:44.406
Just those people who hated each other after coming to Sahaja yoga

00:39:44.403 --> 00:39:46.216
have started loving each other,

00:39:46.216 --> 00:39:48.406
understanding and enjoying each other.

00:39:48.416 --> 00:39:50.916
And married life in Sahaja Yoga is tremendous.

00:39:50.916 --> 00:39:56.926
Ninety percent of married life is so great that people in America

00:39:56.926 --> 00:39:59.426
where they divorce third year, every third year,

00:39:59.406 --> 00:40:03.106
we have seen people are doing very well in the married life

00:40:03.106 --> 00:40:05.404
even in America.

00:40:09.893 --> 00:40:12.393
Even here the…you see this mental projection,

00:40:12.393 --> 00:40:15.113
the wife is no good, the husband no good, all vanishes.

00:40:15.113 --> 00:40:17.613
You become the Spirit. You start enjoying

00:40:17.613 --> 00:40:22.373
the deeper significance of marriage.

00:40:22.363 --> 00:40:26.253
Then comes the fourth side of the Lakshmi Tattwa

00:40:26.253 --> 00:40:31.521
Is the fourth side is the ascending side.

00:40:31.530 --> 00:40:35.504
The people who have got more money are fed up

00:40:35.482 --> 00:40:38.104
and now want to have something beyond.

00:40:38.112 --> 00:40:43.094
In the same way in Sahaja Yoga, when you start moving

00:40:43.099 --> 00:40:47.933
then you find that nothing but spiritual life gives you real joy

00:40:47.943 --> 00:40:52.013
So you just don’t care for anything else but the spiritual life.

00:40:52.013 --> 00:40:54.513
And what is the spiritual life of Sahaja Yoga is

00:40:54.513 --> 00:40:55.963
that you become the light

00:40:55.963 --> 00:40:57.775
and you give light to others.

00:40:57.766 --> 00:41:01.593
Selflessly, there is no selfish motive in it.

00:41:01.593 --> 00:41:03.145
Just because you are the light,

00:41:03.124 --> 00:41:04.302
you become the light,

00:41:04.284 --> 00:41:06.622
You don't see the light, you become the light.

00:41:06.614 --> 00:41:10.382
And you give light to others and just do it selflessly,

00:41:10.414 --> 00:41:12.232
without charging any money.

00:41:12.232 --> 00:41:13.672
Without asking for anything

00:41:13.672 --> 00:41:17.512
you just start giving what you have got.

00:41:17.502 --> 00:41:20.662
Spontaneously without paying for it

00:41:20.646 --> 00:41:24.882
You just do it in a way that is a saintly way.

00:41:24.904 --> 00:41:28.130
Saints always spend their own money,

00:41:28.130 --> 00:41:30.394
always have spent their own money

00:41:30.418 --> 00:41:32.511
to give joy to others.

00:41:32.502 --> 00:41:34.300
They have never taken money from anyone.

00:41:34.313 --> 00:41:35.991
I mean I have not heard of any saint

00:41:35.967 --> 00:41:38.467
who has built up big palaces

00:41:38.479 --> 00:41:40.979
and big places and big organisation, never.

00:41:40.979 --> 00:41:43.161
That's not a sign of a saint.

00:41:43.173 --> 00:41:48.443
A saint just emits compassion

00:41:48.443 --> 00:41:52.613
and this compassion doesn’t speak. It is silent.

00:41:52.613 --> 00:41:55.303
This compassion acts.

00:41:55.302 --> 00:41:57.802
It doesn’t speak. It acts.

00:41:57.802 --> 00:42:01.662
When it acts it works out wonders.

00:42:01.662 --> 00:42:03.682
That's what you know when Christ

00:42:03.682 --> 00:42:05.192
was touched by some lady

00:42:05.176 --> 00:42:08.701
he said, "Some energy has flown through Me."

00:42:08.701 --> 00:42:09.992
That is what it is.

00:42:09.989 --> 00:42:12.489
That the energy starts flowing through you

00:42:12.489 --> 00:42:14.020
and you do not do anything

00:42:14.054 --> 00:42:15.710
just happens automatically.

00:42:15.691 --> 00:42:18.191
Without doing anything you achieve it.

00:42:18.191 --> 00:42:19.581
So for today

00:42:19.581 --> 00:42:22.491
I think I have come up to the Nabhi Chakra.

00:42:22.490 --> 00:42:24.990
tomorrow I'll tell you about other chakras

00:42:25.028 --> 00:42:31.190
in better, elaborate way

00:42:31.190 --> 00:42:32.592
that you will understand

00:42:32.591 --> 00:42:34.982
what is the essence of these chakras.

00:42:34.984 --> 00:42:36.901
That what becomes of you.

00:42:36.901 --> 00:42:38.724
They have described to you the chakras

00:42:38.724 --> 00:42:40.161
but why these chakras.

00:42:40.157 --> 00:42:41.501
What do they mean?

00:42:41.481 --> 00:42:42.384
These are the different,

00:42:42.386 --> 00:42:45.214
evolutionary milestones within us,

00:42:45.201 --> 00:42:48.037
which have been crossed and the last one

00:42:48.035 --> 00:42:50.908
is this one, which you have to cross now. That's all.

00:42:50.917 --> 00:42:52.978
See you are just ready for it.

00:42:52.987 --> 00:42:55.948
You are made for this. God has made you for this.

00:42:55.948 --> 00:42:59.128
Its best is that you get to it.

00:42:59.128 --> 00:43:03.158
And that’s why I was yesterday asking questions

00:43:03.148 --> 00:43:04.168
and people have now told Me,

00:43:04.168 --> 00:43:06.668
“Mother please don’t ask questions because it is a waste

00:43:06.668 --> 00:43:08.458
it’s a waste of time.”

00:43:08.458 --> 00:43:10.728
Those people who are asking questions

00:43:10.728 --> 00:43:12.568
are not asking any sensible questions.

00:43:12.568 --> 00:43:14.048
They are not bothered about themselves

00:43:14.058 --> 00:43:16.042
why, how they are spending their lives.

00:43:16.042 --> 00:43:16.688
of course some people

00:43:16.682 --> 00:43:18.528
asked very sensible questions also

00:43:18.538 --> 00:43:21.038
I must say, but there’s no need to ask questions.

00:43:21.048 --> 00:43:23.138
Let us see if it works out within in you.

00:43:23.138 --> 00:43:26.058
If it works out it will be a good idea.

00:43:26.058 --> 00:43:32.410
Now you want to have Realisation first?
